{"tid":204293,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一唔開心身體就會痛","createTime":"2017-04-17T02:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T10:49:26.000Z","uid":28614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5626440e09353a77620957bfa96ee0af54f12b0f","tid":204293,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"每次一唔開心緊張崩潰<br />\n就會胃痛腸痛食唔到野<br />\n有次唔知係咪谷得太勁<br />\n釋放唔到，心都痛撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有辨法解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好撚辛苦，好想去自殺<br />\n唔好叫我放鬆d，放鬆到我就唔洗問人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339d5fba0bcc2ac3c58bae998b83c6c5ffb9b40a","tid":204293,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:25:48.000Z","msg":"依家一傷心唔知點解好難喊<br />\n一定要谷到爆先肯大喊9叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df346bd981be1055f74cc378c546b0a119d5603d","tid":204293,"uid":62859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"Same<br />\n一唔開心就會胃痛到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c6e07eb913ca4c89a57f64d992fe790f3a248e","tid":204293,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"跑步囉"},{"pid":"a147cc44cd1ffccc0ba0d42a12c87998d00573a3","tid":204293,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"我係成身d肉都會酸痛<br />\n真係好唔開心好心痛果陣"},{"pid":"04706977f6d1a80a30ea0594e1e73f1bfb20166c","tid":204293,"uid":53972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:06:23.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n胸口會魏住咁，同埋會無胃口同係咁作嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1200ab9a8f05063997cfe910aa637331263c7d7d","tid":204293,"uid":58623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,